  <h4 class="author-name"><a href="https://washingtonmonthly.com/people/claire-kelloway/">Claire Kelloway</a></h4>


<p class="bio">Claire Kelloway is a reporter and researcher with the Open Markets Institute and the primary writer for Food & Power, a website covering corporate concentration in the food system. Her writing on food and agriculture has appeared in ProPublica, Civil Eats, Pacific Standard, and more.</p></div>
  
